I'm back raising funds for @specialolympicsco with my custom practice glove that supports an organization near to me and Ashley's hearts. I'll be giving away some cool prizes the rest of the season. ALL donations gain entries into the grand prize drawing at the end of the season of this glove, signed by me! For this first raffle, one winner will be drawn to win four tickets and batting practice passes to any remaining @Rockies game, home or away. Just click the link in my bio to donate and enter!

I am honored to once again be nominated for the Roberto Clemente Award by the @Rockies... THANK YOU! To celebrate, I'm holding another raffle. Two of the game's best - @shoheiohtani and fellow nominee @miketrout - donated signed balls to benefit @specialolympicsco. ALL proceeds benefit SOCO! I'll draw one random winner for each ball on Monday. To enter, click the link in my bio!
